\" style=\"top:12.348564347420554%;left:39.61892155949076%;animation-delay:4.33734996243466s;animation-duration:7.752661787498931s\"></div><div class=\"particle\" style=\"top:18.27195174453331%;left:8.967194338397967%;animation-delay:4.754291259461153s;animation-duration:4.922750903548251s\"></div><div class=\"particle\" style=\"top:27.43882797256534%;left:50.570010965321764%;animation-delay:4.964020071172394s;animation-duration:4.636476267172562s\"></div><div class=\"particle\" style=\"top:49.6943773832018%;left:82.0293965962841%;animation-delay:3.8290722749791235s;animation-duration:5.527596509822453s\"></div><div class=\"particle\" style=\"top:73.3475384009364%;left:14.498567539797591%;animation-delay:1.0030079150786406s;animation-duration:6.275706109499375s\"></div><div class=\"particle\" style=\"top:70.36331963313233%;left:26.01584676263613%;animation-delay:1.1615236603071848s;animation-duration:6.258585400149997s\"></div><div class=\"particle\" style=\"top:29.84064730813656%;left:44.89787435611498%;animation-delay:3.075891309398599s;animation-duration:6.134308087321701s\"></div><div class=\"particle\" style=\"top:58.255128985434034%;left:2.904554030262174%;animation-delay:4.927324713568234s;animation-duration:5.192119883605141s\"></div><div class=\"particle\" style=\"top:82.35577701795336%;left:13.62913532587815%;animation-delay:2.0942985976777475s;animation-duration:4.956059587250121s\"></div></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 text-center\"><div class=\"space-y-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"flex justify-center mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.5)\"><div class=\"relative w-64 h-64 sm:w-80 sm:h-80 md:w-96 md:h-96 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"><img alt=\"Querido Camp Logo\" fetchPriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain drop-shadow-2xl\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/logo.png\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 blur-3xl -z-10 animate-pulse\"></div></div></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-full px-8 py-3 inline-block border border-primary/20\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><span class=\"text-primary font-semibold text-lg\">Conheça todos os detalhes do Querido Camp</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0)\"><div class=\"glass-card w-16 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary/30\"></div><div class=\"glass-card w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-primary/20\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full animate-pulse\"></div></div><div class=\"glass-card w-16 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary/30\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1200 120\" class=\"w-full h-20 fill-current text-primary/10\"><path d=\"M0,60 C300,120 900,0 1200,60 L1200,120 L0,120 Z\"></path></svg></div></div><section class=\"py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-black to-gray-900\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"relative group glass-gold glass-hover glass-shine rounded-2xl overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full\"><div class=\"p-8\"><p class=\"text-white text-lg mb-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">O Querido Camp é um campeonato de Counter-Strike 2 criado com o objetivo de impulsionar e fortalecer ainda mais o cenário competitivo em Sergipe. Buscamos proporcionar uma experiência de alto nível para jogadores e times que querem testar suas habilidades, competir em um ambiente estruturado e, acima de tudo, evoluir dentro do cenário de esports!</p><p class=\"text-white text-lg mb-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Nesta edição, contamos com ainda mais apoiadores que acreditam no nosso potencial e compartilham da nossa visão de crescimento. Estamos focados em tornar o Querido Camp um evento cada vez maior, mais organizado e competitivo, oferecendo uma plataforma para que talentos locais se destaquem e alcancem novos patamares.</p><p class=\"text-white text-lg mb-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Nossa missão é elevar o nível do CS2 em Sergipe, criando oportunidades para jogadores de todos os níveis e promovendo a comunidade local de esports. Acreditamos que com dedicação, organização e paixão pelo jogo, podemos construir um cenário competitivo forte e sustentável em nossa região.</p><p class=\"text-white text-lg\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Junte-se a nós nesta jornada e faça parte da história do Querido Camp!</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold/20 via-gold/40 to-gold/20 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm -z-10\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 bg-black\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gold mb-8 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Formato do Campeonato</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"relative group glass-gold glass-hover glass-shine rounded-2xl overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full\"><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gold mb-4\">Fase de Grupos</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-white\"><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-gold mr-2\">•</span><span>Vitória por mapa vale 3 pontos</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-gold mr-2\">•</span><span>MD2</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-gold mr-2\">•</span><span>Todos jogam contra todos</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-gold mr-2\">•</span><span>Os 8 melhores avançam para as quartas de final</span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold/20 via-gold/40 to-gold/20 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm -z-10\"></div></div><div class=\"relative group glass-gold glass-hover glass-shine rounded-2xl overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full\"><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gold mb-4\">Critérios de Desempate</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-white\"><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-gold mr-2\">1.</span><span>Saldo de rounds</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-gold mr-2\">2.</span><span>Confronto direto</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-gold mr-2\">3.</span><span>Maior número de rounds vencidos</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-gold mr-2\">4.</span><span>Menor número de rounds perdidos</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-gold mr-2\">5.</span><span>Sorteio</span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold/20 via-gold/40 to-gold/20 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm -z-10\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-black to-gray-900\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gold mb-10 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Cronograma do Campeonato</h2><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"relative border-l-2 border-gold pl-8 space-y-10\"><div class=\"relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute -left-10 mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gold\"></div><h3 class=\"text-gold font-bold text-lg\">Até 15 de Janeiro</h3><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mt-1\">Inscrições</h4><p class=\"text-gray-300 mt-2\">Período de inscrições para equipes e jogadores individuais.</p></div><div class=\"relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute -left-10 mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gold\"></div><h3 class=\"text-gold font-bold text-lg\">19 de Janeiro de 2026</h3><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mt-1\">Início do Campeonato</h4><p class=\"text-gray-300 mt-2\">Cerimônia de abertura e primeiras partidas da fase de grupos.</p></div><div class=\"relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute -left-10 mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gold\"></div><h3 class=\"text-gold font-bold text-lg\">19 de Janeiro a 13 de Fevereiro</h3><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mt-1\">Fase de Grupos</h4><p class=\"text-gray-300 mt-2\">Partidas da fase de grupos, com jogos de ida e volta. Todos jogam contra todos.</p></div><div class=\"relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute -left-10 mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gold\"></div><h3 class=\"text-gold font-bold text-lg\">14 de Fevereiro a 23 de Fevereiro</h3><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mt-1\">Pausa - Carnaval</h4><p class=\"text-gray-300 mt-2\">Pausa no campeonato devido ao período de carnaval.</p></div><div class=\"relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute -left-10 mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gold\"></div><h3 class=\"text-gold font-bold text-lg\">24 de Fevereiro a 5 de Março</h3><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mt-1\">Quartas e Semifinais (Online)</h4><p class=\"text-gray-300 mt-2\">Confrontos eliminatórios entre os 8 melhores times nas quartas de final, seguido pelas semifinais entre os 4 times restantes.</p></div><div class=\"relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute -left-10 mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gold\"></div><h3 class=\"text-gold font-bold text-lg\">7 e 8 de Março</h3><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mt-1\">Finais Presenciais</h4><p class=\"text-gray-300 mt-2\">Grande final presencial em LAN e cerimônia de premiação.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 bg-black\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"relative  glass-gold glass-hover glass-shine rounded-2xl overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full\"><div class=\"p-8 text-center\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gold mb-6\">Pronto para participar?</h2><p class=\"text-white mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Não perca a oportunidade de fazer parte do maior campeonato de CS2 de Sergipe. Inscreva-se agora!</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\"><a class=\"border-2 border-gold text-gold font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-md hover:bg-gold/10 transition-colors transform hover:scale-105 duration-200 shadow-lg shadow-gold/10\" href=\"/regras\">Ver Regras</a><a class=\"bg-gold text-black font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-md hover:bg-gold/80 transition-colors transform hover:scale-105 duration-200 shadow-lg shadow-gold/20\" href=\"/inscricao\">Fazer Inscrição - R$ 75,00</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-gray-900 pt-16 pb-8 border-t border-gold/10\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><section class=\"mb-20\"><h3 class=\"text-center text-gray-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-12\" style=\"opacity:0\">Patrocinadores &amp; Parceiros</h3><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-